	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=/db/item.html?item=14609&mid=107156368751067>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=/db/item.html?item=14609&mid=107156368751067>Range</a> <a id=fs8 href=/db/item.html?item=14609&mid=107156368751067#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Tue, Dec 16th 3:35 AM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=88524><span id= >Loviotor</span></a><br><span id=notbold>21 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Having played a ranger since I started playing EQ, I can confirm that the range = bow+arrow, just as the damage - bow+arrow.<br><br>Therefore, with my current bow/arrows, I get the following<br><br>Bow Damage = <b>33</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrow Damage = <b>11</b><br>Total Damage = <b>44</b><br><br>Bow Range = <b>250</b>  Arrow Range = <b>170</b><br>Total Range = <b>420</b><br><br>That is with a Warmaster Recurve Longbow and Blessed Champion Arrows.<br><br>Normal crits for max of 974, Trueshot crits for 1980ish.<br><br>On the subject of the Shissar Bane weapons, previous comments are correct, using a bow against the Emperor would be worthless, as they usually corner him, not only wall him (if he was merely walled, I could actually hit him with proper positioning), therefore making attempting to hit with a bow next to worthless.  You may end up getting a few shots in, but nowhere near what you will be able to do DPS-wise with 1hs or even 2hs weapons, as a ranger.<br>Just my 2cp worth.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec 16 03:44:24 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
